wrapScienceJ.process

Class GenericProcessSequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • wrapScienceJ.process.GenericProcessNode
      • wrapScienceJ.process.GenericProcessSequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericProcess, InputOutputPolicy, GenericImageProcess, PolicyImageStorage

    public abstract class GenericProcessSequence
extends GenericProcessNode
implements GenericImageProcess
    Abstract Base class to implement processes involving an image. Typically, this is used to implement plugins such as ImageJ plugins using the WrapImaJ API and ImageCore to encode an image.
